  <brief_title>A Phase 1 Pharmacokinetic Study of Single-Ascending Doses of Intravenous Nafithromycin in Healthy Adult Subjects</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 1, Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled, Safety, Tolerability, and Pharmacokinetic Study of Single-Ascending Doses of Intravenous Nafithromycin in Healthy Adult Subjects</official_title>
  <sponsors>
